<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title lang="ko"></title>

</head>
<body>

  <!-- Clubs -->
  <section id="clubs" class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <header class="section__header">
        <h2 class="section__title mb-3">
          <span class="section__category mb-2" lang="en">Mentors</span>
          각 분야 최고의 멘토들
        </h2>
        <p class="section__text">
          현재 Profolio에서 첨삭을 담당해주시는<br>
          멘토들을 소개합니다!
        </p>
      </header>
      <div class="cards row">
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-3 mb-md-0">
            <%= image_tag "programmer.jpg", :class=>"card-img-top"  %>
            <!-- <img class="card-img-top"
                 src="assets/item-1@1x.jpg"
                 alt> -->
            <div class="card-block">
              <h4 class="card-title mb-2">개발자</h4>
              <p class="card-text">
                서울대 컴퓨터공학과 학사<br>
                멋쟁이 사자처럼 대표
              </p>
              <a href="" class="btn btn-primary bg-primary">첨삭요청</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
          <div class="card mb-3 mb-md-0">
            <%= image_tag "design.jpg", :class=>"card-img-top"  %>
            <div class="card-block">
              <h4 class="card-title mb-2">디자인</h4>
              <p class="card-text">
                삼성 UX 디자이너<br>
                올해의 디자이너상 수상
              </p>
              <a href="" class="btn btn-primary bg-primary">첨삭요청</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 col-md-4">
          <div class="card">
            <%= image_tag "planning.jpg", :class=>"card-img-top"  %>
            <div class="card-block">
              <h4 class="card-title mb-2">기획</h4>
              <p class="card-text">
                멋쟁이 사자처럼 3기<br>
                Gudak 기획팀 팀장
              </p>
              <a href="" class="btn btn-primary bg-primary">첨삭요청</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
  <!-- // Clubs -->

</body>
</html>
